[Installation](#installation) - [Usage](#usage) - [Latest changes](#latest-changes) - [Versioning](#versioning) - [Support and contributing](#support-and-contributing)## Installation```bashpython -m pip install botocore-stubs```## UsageUse [mypy](https://github.com/python/mypy) or [pyright](https://github.com/microsoft/pyright) for type checking.### Latest changesFull changelog can be found in [Releases](https://github.com/youtype/botocore-stubs/releases).## Versioning`botocore-stubs` version is the same as related `botocore` version and follows[PEP 440](https://www.python.org/dev/peps/pep-0440/) format.## Support and contributingPlease reports any bugs or request new features in[botocore-stubs](https://github.com/youtype/botocore-stubs/issues/) repository.
